data.description:
Wonderful opportunity for nicely updated Richfield home. This move-in ready property features a newly
remodeled full bathroom, finished lower level with egress window (4th Bdrm), hardwood floors, new
exterior paint, and spacious 2-car garage. Convenient location near highways, shopping, restaurants, and
more.
